 not mean to imply that soloing was not something capable of enchanters, mearly to say that we could be providing so much more to the playing experience of 5 other people.<br><br>Well whatever you decide to do, Enjoy it ;)<br><br>and as for the original poster, I hope you got my message that you won't go wrong either way, and that either way you will be happy.  And if you are ever grouped with an enchanter that chose differently than you, mearly let him cast the mez spells, or you take charge of the mez spells, but again its all just relative to your position.</p>&nbsp;<br>Ezzlan 25th ENC Brell<br>Antarius 35th Bard Terris-Thule</td></td></tr>
